decks.notes: The deck focuses on utilizing Vohar, Vodalian Desecrator as the commander to aggressively control the game by utilizing a mix of removal, disruption, and graveyard manipulation to overwhelm opponents. It aims to quickly establish board presence with powerful creatures like Archon of Cruelty and Griselbrand, while also disrupting opponents' strategies with cards like Thoughtseize and Force of Will. The deck also utilizes reanimation spells like Animate Dead and Necromancy to bring back key threats from the graveyard. By combining aggressive creatures with disruptive spells and graveyard recursion, the deck seeks to maintain pressure on opponents and secure victory through overwhelming board presence and disruption.
